<reference id="reference_F16A859F9B0E426B8BB110ECFA794EAA"><title><keyword
            >plus-eclipsehelp-topics-twopass</keyword></title><abstract>
        <shortdesc>The <keyword>plus-eclipsehelp-topics-twopass</keyword> plugin extends the
                <keyword>eclipsehelp+</keyword> transtype by processing topics in two XSLT stages.
            While this has no effect in itself, it permits other plugins to insert processing
            between the stages.</shortdesc>
        <p>Stage 1 performs most processing, producing XHTML as the <keyword>basic</keyword> topic
            processing in <keyword>eclipsehelp+</keyword> does. Stage 2 is an identity
            transformation. Plugins can add processing to stage 1 or stage 2, adding processing
            between the stages if the final XHTML requires results from the intermediate processing.</p>
        <p>This plugin does not affect map processing.</p>
    </abstract><refbody>
        <section id="section_1ED97B49069548D2931AC1152152F57B">
